This route is a popular route amongst youngsters who like biking to places to do beer tasting. The ride from downtown to North Van is definitely not that easy, but you will be rewarded with a beautiful view along the way!
This is one of the hardest biking routes in Vancouver. It is located in North Van. If you like challenge, you will definitely enjoy it!
A biking route with a stunning sea view. A super easy and chill ride. If you would like to have a bit of longer ride, hop onto the Stanley Park biking route. You will definitely enjoy it!

This is a route that lots of people choose to bike on. This definitely tough, the elevation is 1000m. If you would like to try it out, make sure you have plenty of snacks packed to charge you up on your way up to the mountain.

This is a city road route. With the best designed biking lanes in the world, you can enjoy your biking in the city of Vancouver without any concerns! Enjoy your ride and enjoy our beautiful city view!
